      {
        "type": "break"
      },
      {
        "type": "break"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "value": "Brother."
      },
      {
        "type": "break"
      },
      {
        "type": "break"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "value": "Germany has been in and out of recession for two years. Volkswagen was closing factories. Energy costs cratered the industrial base before a single Iranian mine hit the water."
      },
      {
        "type": "break"
      },
      {
        "type": "break"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "value": "The momentum he is referring to is currently undetected by all known measuring instruments."
      },
      {
        "type": "break"
      },
      {
        "type": "break"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "value": "The Iran war found it anyway. Somehow."
      }
